sniff1: a minimal libpcap program that prints packet lengths
sniff2: can read packets from interface or from pcap file
sniff3: compiles a filter expression
sniff4: filter expression hardcoded from tcpdump -dd 
sniff5: decode link level, ip and udp or tcp header 
sniff6: gather interface statistics periodically

Perl samples using Net::Pcap binding
-------------------------------------------------------------
sniff.pl:  minimal sniffer program
sniffw.pl: minimal sniffer that also writes a pcap
gen_pcap.pl: write a pcap (non-IP) of ascii "packets"
